      "TextTw": "",
      "TextEn": "",
      "VoiceJp": "https://r2.rikaaa0928.moe/ba-story-viewer/tts/group/1101/lines/0058.mp3",
      "TextJpVoice": "[mischievous]でしたら、これはどうでしょう？"
